name: FastProxyChecker
body:
### Welcome to FastProxyChecker!
FastProxyChecker is a php tool designed to help the task of checking proxies, with maximum accuracy and performance. The tool supports all kinds of proxies, multi-threading, using files, and many other features.

### How do I use it, and where do I get the code?
The best way to get the stable `Version 1.2` is to download it straight from GitHub Pages (Download button above).
The docs are available [here](https://github.com/samuel-allan/FastProxyChecker/tree/v1.2).
Currently the best version to use is `Version 1.2` which has new features, and holds strong against bugs.

### All Versions Table
Version number | Working | Bug Rating | Documentation
----------- | ----------- | ----------- | -----------
Version 1.2 | Yes | Stable | [V1.2 Release](https://github.com/samuel-allan/FastProxyChecker/tree/v1.2)
Version 1.1 | Yes | Stable | [V1.1 Folder](https://github.com/samuel-allan/FastProxyChecker/blob/master/Version%201.1/Documentation)
Version 1.0 | N/A | No Support | [Old Docs](https://github.com/samuel-allan/FastProxyChecker/blob/master/Version%201/Documentation.txt)
